Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy.bpr

Loading and reading BPR deployment archives during process deployment.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IAeBpr Interface for wrapping the deployment of a BPR.
IAeBprAccessor Represents the strategy for accessing resources within a bpr deployment.
 

Class Summary
AeAbstractBprStrategy Base class for IAeBprStrategy implementations.
AeBpr Standard IAeBpr impl for BPR archive file deployments.
AeBprContext Provides access to deployment context resources.
AeBprDeploymentSource Wraps the deployment of a single pdd from the BPR archive.
AeJarFileBprAccessor A IAeBprFileStrategy impl where bpr resources are pulled from directly from the archive file.
AeJarFileBprAccessor.AeNameFilter Convience class - impl of FilenameFilter for building deployment descriptor object.
AeTempFileUploadHandler Default implementation of IAeFileUploadHandler.
AeUnpackedBprAccessor A IAeBprFileStrategy impl where bpr resources are pulled from an unpacked copy of the original bpr file.
AeUnpackedBprContext Allows short name to be specified in x-tor.
 

Package org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy.bpr Description

Loading and reading BPR deployment archives during process deployment.
